ousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/good-character-heaviest-mizan\/","url_meta":{"origin":40096,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character is heaviest on the Scale","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing is heavier upon the scale of a believer on the Day of Resurrection than his good character. Verily, Allah hates the vulgar and obscene.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2002 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/most-beloved-best-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":40096,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: The Prophet&#8217;s beloved have best character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I tell you about the most beloved to me and the closest to my assembly on the Day of Resurrection? Those with the best character.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 272 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34598,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/11\/29\/tyrants-will-be-trampled\/","url_meta":{"origin":40096,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Arrogance: Tyrants are trampled on the Day of Resurrection","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe arrogant and the tyrants will be gathered on the Day of Resurrection as tiny particles. The people will trample upon them due to their disgrace before Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: al-Taw\u0101\u1e0du\u2019 wal-Khum\u016bl 224 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14898,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/10\/overeating-hungriest-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":40096,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Gluttony: Those who overate will be hungriest in Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the people who ate to their fill the most in this world will be the hungriest on the Day of Resurrection.\" Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3351 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u